snippet.title: Moonray // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
**Note: this is pre-alpha footage and may not be included in final release**

Coming to Steam Early Access on July 2nd, 2020

Moonray is an intense action RPG with stunning surreal visuals and a world-class sound track by Ten Walls

Learn more at moonray.game
